text: Bùi Thị Ngà (born August 15, 1994 in Ninh BìnhBùi Thị Ngà: Nữ tuyển thủ Quốc gia gốc Ninh Bình ) is a member of the Vietnam women's national volleyball team.Người đẹp trên sàn đấu (kỳ 45): Chân bóng chuyền dài nhất Đông Nam Á == Career == Ngà played with the club Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank.Linh Chi, Bùi Thị Ngà sắp sang Thái thi đấu == Clubs == * Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank == Awards == === Individual === * 2013 VTV Cup Championship "Best Blocker" * 2014 VTV Binh Dien International Cup "Best Blocker" * 2014 VTV Binh Dien International Cup "Best Spiker" * 2014 VTV Cup Championship "Best Blocker" * 2018 VTV Cup Championship "Best Middle Blocker" ===Clubs=== * 2012 Vietnam League - 16px Champion, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank * 2013 Vietnam League - 16px Champion, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank * 2014 Vietnam League - 16px Champion, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank * 2015 Vietnam League - 16px Champion, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank * 2016 Vietnam League - 16px Runner-Up, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank * 2017 Vietnam League - 16px Runner-Up, with Thông tin Liên Việt Post Bank ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese women's volleyball players Category:People from Ninh Bình Province Category:Vietnam women's international volleyball players Category:Southeast Asian Games silver medalists for Vietnam Category:Southeast Asian Games bronze medalists for Vietnam Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in volleyball Category:Competitors at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games Category:Volleyball players at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games Category:Middle blockers
